@*
Displays a form for users to submit a new movie.
Displays the heading "Add Movie Form" using an h2 tag.
Provides a form for users to enter the movie details:
Title: Input field for the movie name with associated validation messages.
Director: Input field for the director name with associated validation messages.
Genre: Input field for the genre with associated validation messages. 
Rating: Input field for the movie rating with associated validation messages.
The "Add Movie" button allows users to submit the form, styled with the class btn btn-primary.
